how to cook.

117
00:06:01,143 --> 00:06:03,188
But I could teach you.

118
00:06:03,232 --> 00:06:07,323
You know what they say
about too many cooks.

119
00:06:07,367 --> 00:06:09,934
You could do anything
you want.

120
00:06:09,978 --> 00:06:12,850
