172
00:08:36,516 --> 00:08:38,561
Hi.

173
00:08:38,605 --> 00:08:41,477
I'm Alexander Dante.

174
00:08:41,521 --> 00:08:43,740
You're a man.

175
00:08:43,784 --> 00:08:46,221
