- Thanks.

242
00:11:49,534 --> 00:11:53,408
Hmm. Male secretary?

243
00:11:53,451 --> 00:11:56,019
- Men type faster.
- Huh?

244
00:11:56,063 --> 00:11:58,587
- Shorter nails.
